page.title: 18SUPERNATURAL
page.content: yes no Are you superstitious? 66% 34% If you broke a mirror would it mean 7 years bad luck? 22% 78% Would you walk under a ladder? 55% 45% Do you cut your toe nails on a Friday 42% 21% If a black cat crossed your path would it mean bad luck? 15% 85% If you upset the salt do you pick it up and throw it over your shoulder? 42% 58% Have you a lucky number? 40% 60% Do you read the 'stars' in newspapers and magazines? 39% 61% Do you hang up a new corn dolly each year? 7% 93% Would you hang up a horse shoe to bring you luck? 47% 53%
